Unit Name: Nomad Sari On the Med Collection - Pario - Turquoise & Gold Fish Design
Webpage description (html):
Bring a breath of fresh ocean energy into your product range with the Turquoise & Gold Fish Handpainted Pario from the Nomad Sari Collection – where artisan tradition meets coastal boho flair.

Hand-dyed, block printed, and handpainted by skilled Indian artisans, each pario features golden fish motifs on a rich turquoise backdrop. A truly unique piece that channels sun-soaked days, ocean breezes, and effortless summer style.

Product Features:

  • One-of-a-Kind Craftsmanship – Each pario is tie-dyed, block printed, and handpainted with shimmering gold fish details.

  • Multi-Use Styling – Wear as a sarong, beach dress, wrap, scarf, or light throw.

  • Ethically Made – Created in collaboration with artisan families in India, supporting traditional techniques and fair working conditions.

  • Large & Versatile – Approx. 110 x 180 cm – ideal for all body types and styling preferences.

  • Perfect for Resale – Supplied in assorted coastal-inspired designs. A great fit for boutiques, beachwear shops, wellness spaces, and slow fashion retailers.

Why Choose the Nomad Sari Collection?

These parios combine sustainable craftsmanship with bold, free-spirited design. Perfect for customers who appreciate handmade pieces, ethical sourcing, and a story behind their style.

Dropshipping Ready Fast shipping from UK & EU warehouses. Support fair trade. Share artisan-made fashion. Stand out with Nomad Sari.
